text: I’m working on refilling and giving to those who deserve it. I can’t continue to share my light with everyone.

author: 👑 Chaunti 👑
text: I don’t regret ever giving my love, time, and attention to people. I just hope I can learn to give ONLY when I can and to those that will release it back. Love and energy is endless but I need to save some for myself. It needs to be recharged.

author: 👑 Chaunti 👑
text: I was always told to give when I could but I wasn’t able to differentiate between when I could and when I knew someone needed it. The small amount of energy I have left just to survive I give to make others happy.
